{"tid":346343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［隨機殺人］北投女童割喉兇手免死 女童舅舅：台灣就是鬼島","createTime":"2017-08-04T00:43:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-04T03:22:21.000Z","uid":41351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"017186912d5c834879ad76cc567ff89ffb90eeab","tid":346343,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T00:43:38.000Z","msg":"龔姓男子前年進入北投國小，持菜刀在女廁殺害劉姓女童，送醫搶救仍宣告不治，最高法院今判無期徒刑，褫奪公權終身定讞。女童舅舅今天回應，尚未聯繫到女童父母，家屬當然覺得不合理、不公平，「台灣就是鬼島，那又如何？我們也沒辦法改變什麼」。<br />\n<br />\n他說，家屬本來就覺得他該被判死刑，不可能也不知道要怎麼原諒他。女童父母完全不想得知這方面的訊息，「因為我們不想影響原本的生活」。<br />\n<br />\n龔稱，「耳朵旁常聽到有人在罵他」，前年5月下午翻進北投國小，摀住女童口鼻，持菜刀砍殺女童脖子，事後他報警坦承殺人。一、二審皆認為龔有精神疾病，沒判死刑。最高法院今駁回上訴，依成年人故意對兒童犯殺人罪，判龔無期徒刑定讞。<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7315/2621660\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7315%2F2621660&d=5HBBM7S7erSiSLv4VqhfqpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=39cacfdf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7315/2621660</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/04/084219_34da4de9bf68a8d65293893108987360.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F04%2F084219_34da4de9bf68a8d65293893108987360.jpg&h=56196147&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/04/084329_1576d9dcb1515a10385878b866e1c289.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F04%2F084329_1576d9dcb1515a10385878b866e1c289.jpg&h=e4ea38a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鬼島"},{"pid":"e7316c43c6e4ccb0ebc6ec167f79d7eae0e0a16a","tid":346343,"uid":29514,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T00:48:16.000Z","msg":"坐成世慘過死刑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbfc802109bcec35bde235f65f3c5295601d3b01","tid":346343,"uid":15336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T00:54:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>坐成世慘過死刑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n傻啦 無期徒刑坐廿年多啲就出返黎啦"},{"pid":"fbd02a07191aec69c1fd32d67570c30e65890446","tid":346343,"uid":15592,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T00:54:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>坐成世慘過死刑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但家屬未必咁諗<br />\n次次諗起死者, 都會聯想到個兇手係監獄un un 腳, 包食住<br />\n而自己仲可能有份俾稅養緊個犯, 都咪話唔難受"},{"pid":"1534d60d3673e2d1bdc2108129211ee3c9461e78","tid":346343,"uid":116704,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T01:10:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>坐成世慘過死刑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n傻啦 無期徒刑坐廿年多啲就出返黎啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當廿年，出返嚟其實已經2個世界。<br />\n<br />\n講刑罰我都認為坐監大過死刑，死左一了百了"},{"pid":"a71760cd617eeaf4707c928bf4865d09280e9a48","tid":346343,"uid":15336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T01:14:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>坐成世慘過死刑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n傻啦 無期徒刑坐廿年多啲就出返黎啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當廿年，出返嚟其實已經2個世界。<br />\n<br />\n講刑罰我都認為坐監大過死刑，死左一了百了</blockquote><br />\n對個社會黎講<br />\n一個殺人犯 廿年後就可以出返黎大家身邊<br />\n你安心咩？<br />\n我認為坐監係好過死刑 前提係廢除假釋制度"},{"pid":"2ee5a22ea46e8839bde64d88596252b1370820c5","tid":346343,"uid":55453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T01:52:19.000Z","msg":"殺人填命係應該㗎，仲要係個七歲嘅小朋友。將來條友出獄，傳媒又一定再報導，強迫佢哋回憶件事，對死者家屬嚟講根本係再次傷害。"},{"pid":"31d515fbc8db0fa35394558c4993dd79a5c86a80","tid":346343,"uid":41351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T02:13:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>殺人填命係應該㗎，仲要係個七歲嘅小朋友。將來條友出獄，傳媒又一定再報導，強迫佢哋回憶件事，對死者家屬嚟講根本係再次傷害。</blockquote><br />\n條友講明殺人目的求死刑<br />\n出返來做連環殺手都似"},{"pid":"33aa909fba798eacbf45c9865b3c7c8c4ed03afa","tid":346343,"uid":101390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T02:35:18.000Z","msg":"成日話有精神病嘅唔洗死刑<br />\n咁即係痴線佬殺幾多人都得啦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe910e105a79f93ad3a4dfa45eaf2eed467064c8","tid":346343,"uid":35867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T03:19:23.000Z","msg":"點解台灣都叫適合人住，哪怕係窮人，都有呢類人？<br />\n但香港窮人仲慘過台灣，點解咁少random killing?<br />\nso far,都係得一單地鐵放火係廢老做既。<br />\n反而，大圈仔係入境處都殺咗主任級。"},{"pid":"412f23fd44140e0dd9789752eff17dbfedc240e1","tid":346343,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T03:22:21.000Z","msg":"世界上所有廢除死刑嘅先進國家都係鬼國鬼島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n美國加一堆落後國家威權國家先係清泉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}